-- Saskatchewan Could Lose $2 Billion of Revenue, Report Says
-- B y   S i m o n   C a s e y
-- 2010-10-04T15:07:38Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-04/saskatchewan-could-lose-2-billion-of-revenue-report-says.html
BHP Billiton Ltd.’s proposed takeover
of Potash Corp. of Ssskatchewan Inc. could cut the Canadian
province’s revenue by at least $2 billion of the next 10 years,
according to a report by the Conference Board of Canada.  Saskatchewan’s provincial government commented on the
report today in a statement on its website.  To contact the reporter on this story:
